      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">The situation before we started</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-5">The restaurant had been open for a few weeks but did not appear in any local searches. Customers came only from the immediate neighborhood or through direct word of mouth. They had no presence on Google Maps, the logo was temporary, and there was no website.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">The owner knew they needed a digital presence but did not know where to start or what it would cost. They wanted something professional that would work from the first month — without technical complexity on their end.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">What we did</h2>
      <ul class="checklist mb-8">
        <li><strong>Complete and optimized <a href="/en/services/google-business-profile-treasure-coast/" style="color:var(--primary)">Google Business Profile</a></strong> — name, hours, photos, categories, description, and the first batch of local posts.</li>
        <li><strong><a href="/en/services/branding-logo-design-treasure-coast/" style="color:var(--primary)">Logo design and branding</a></strong> — clean, consistent visual identity that works on signage, menus, social media, and print materials.</li>
        <li><strong>Simple, fast <a href="/en/services/web-design-treasure-coast/" style="color:var(--primary)">website</a></strong> — menu, location, hours, visible WhatsApp button, and real photos of the space and team.</li>
        <li>Google Search Console setup and initial local keyword targeting.</li>
        <li>Basic guide for requesting reviews from first customers.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">Results</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-6">The first results appeared within weeks of publishing the profile and website. Detailed metrics are pending confirmation with the client.</p>

